{"tid":959600,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣將iPhone6s reset?","createTime":"2018-12-28T17:29:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T17:59:29.000Z","uid":222332,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8eeaefb102d856fce9320dd09c613c9f4be1f5ca","tid":959600,"uid":222332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T17:29:55.000Z","msg":"之前部 iPhone6s 裂左少少mon<br />\n不過仲用到<br />\n無幾耐唔小心跌左部電話落地下<br />\n個mon爆到點禁都無反應 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住拎去整<br />\n不過整之前 想reset部機<br />\n廢事啲重要資料外洩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嘗試去用iTune reset部機<br />\n但係要喺部機禁allow 先連接到個iTune<br />\n問題係個mon爆到乜都禁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問下點樣可以唔洗喺部電話禁&quot;allow this PC&quot;嗰條問題去用iTune reset部機?<br />\n定係其實係有其他方法？"},{"pid":"03df27d2b7b6f68423575b8de068d2faf7fd331c","tid":959600,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T17:35:35.000Z","msg":"Mouse on iPhone"},{"pid":"fd76480d023cae895870592fc51b13d55e5b2bde","tid":959600,"uid":95172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T17:45:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/surprise_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/surprise_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/surprise_p.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/surprise_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/surprise_y.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c16912cffe71f46d3f5cf0e08e08b69d6ba8ccd","tid":959600,"uid":36673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T17:52:23.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n入recovery mode連itunes整<br />\n但reset=一定要up上最新os <br />\n<a href=\"https://support.apple.com/zh-hk/HT201263\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fzh-hk%2FHT201263&d=kxjFbHuVRxYj3LxnLgn5xkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=0c66cfa2\" target=\"_blank\">https://